I would suggest to accept a IndexGenerator interface, not a IndexFormatter.  IndexFormatter is just a factory to create IndexGenerator, even can be called IndexGeneratorFactory.  So that, in the future, DataStream users can also customize their special index generator. But can also use IndexGeneratorFactory in their DataStream jobs.
interface IndexGenerator extends Serializable {
  String generate(Row row);
}

